When to use SELECT * in PostgreSQL
 
 
 
 
 
In LedgerSMB we use a lot of queries which involve SELECT *.  Many people consider SELECT * harmful but there are several cases where it is useful.  Keep in mind we encapsulate the database behind an API, so SELECT * has different implications than it doe